sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server

    User->>Browser: Open SPA (/exampleapp/spa)
    Browser->>Server: GET /exampleapp/spa
    Server-->>Browser: HTML (SPA shell)

    Browser->>Server: GET main.css
    Server-->>Browser: CSS

    Browser->>Server: GET spa.js
    Server-->>Browser: JavaScript

    Note right of Browser: JS runs and fetches existing notes
    Browser->>Server: GET /api/notes (JSON)
    Server-->>Browser: Notes data

    Note right of Browser: JS renders existing notes

    User->>Browser: Type new note in input
    User->>Browser: Click "Save Note"

    Browser->>Server: POST /api/notes (new note data)
    Server-->>Browser: JSON of created note

    Note right of Browser: JS adds the new note to the displayed list dynamically
